  "remarks": "Assistant Regional Secretary of the Ba’ath Arab Socialist Party since 2005; from 2000 to 2005 Director for the national security of the regional Ba’ath party. Former Governor of Hama (1998-2000). Close associate of President Bashar al-Assad and Maher al-Assad. Senior decision-maker in the regime on repression of civilian population.",
